com.samsung.android.service.health.tracking.data

Class DataPoint

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.samsung.android.service.health.tracking.data.DataPoint

  • public class DataPoint
extends Object
    DataPoint is a map of ValueKey and value with a timestamp.

    Tracking the Galaxy Watch's sensor data is available through HealthTracker.setEventListener(HealthTracker.TrackerEventListener) for a specific HealthTrackerType. Measured sensor data is retrieved with a DataPoint list in HealthTracker.TrackerEventListener.onDataReceived(List<DataPoint>).

    Since:
    1.0.0
    See Also:
    HealthTracker.TrackerEventListener.onDataReceived(List<DataPoint>)
